{"tid":2121323,"cid":38,"subCid":0,"title":"租金連生活雜費月花逾4萬倫敦港人一家三口每月開支一覽","createTime":"2020-07-23T08:43:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-23T09:28:56.000Z","uid":234945,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"8fe8d1ba7a45ef0a06737e7c823c5ece049ed520","tid":2121323,"uid":234945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T08:43:58.000Z","msg":"港人欲透過英國國民（海外）護照（BNO）移居英國，昨（22日）有詳情公布，持BNO的港人明年1月起，可以申請特別簽證留英，並最多可在英國逗留5年，之後可申請居留權，6大申請條件之中，包括需證明有財力留英國生活最少6個月，有居倫敦一家三口公開自己每月生活費逾4萬元，讓有意移居的家庭作參考。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/2703655/?r=mcsdfb\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2703655%2F%3Fr%3Dmcsdfb&d=QJrJoCvBX0rL8AB4Pa6kCFYPZSwMlx1ag7qd%2FaAfmLs%3D&h=729a2313\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/2703655/?r=mcsdfb</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MYAVUXn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMYAVUXn.jpg&h=45f9fef8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n 對比香港好似貴咗啲喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c5a41bd126dbccf826c1decdc1debe1411962a6","tid":2121323,"uid":76344,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T08:48:49.000Z","msg":"而有一家三口居於Zone 6的四房獨立屋<br />\n<br />\n香港四萬夠唔夠租四房？"},{"pid":"aaed73f6b7ef5b64dece9649e2514d9c5c51a669","tid":2121323,"uid":1544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0c5a41bd126dbccf826c1decdc1debe1411962a6","tid":2121323,"uid":76344,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T08:48:49.000Z","msg":"而有一家三口居於Zone 6的四房獨立屋<br />\n<br />\n香港四萬夠唔夠租四房？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T09:22:09.000Z","msg":"香港有兩房住都偷笑"},{"pid":"351d6b261dc3cfb587003ee37dae7d23d4cc6c96","tid":2121323,"uid":10637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0c5a41bd126dbccf826c1decdc1debe1411962a6","tid":2121323,"uid":76344,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T08:48:49.000Z"